00:39:44,674 --> 00:39:46,055
so I talked her up to like a nickel

674
00:39:46,095 --> 00:39:49,257
or maybe even a dime a piece to sand her work,

675
00:39:49,357 --> 00:39:50,877
front, back, and any of the flat edges

676
00:39:50,917 --> 00:39:52,338
on that belt sander that you can see

677
00:39:52,378 --> 00:39:53,339
to the left of the photo.

